FEEL.ST.summary: Feelgood Svenska AB (publ) provides a range of health services to businesses, organizations, and private individuals in Sweden. The company offers health, exercise, and physiotherapy services. Feelgood Svenska AB (publ) was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
